reviewText: It took more than a month and a half for this DVD to arrive to Moscow. And finally there were no english subtitles in the menu of the disc. Despite the fact that it is printed on the DVD box cover and it was in the product description that it contains english subtitles. So be careful!
Need Alexander Skarsgard movies in DVD format 4 please so we can watch them down under

very interesting movie, i liked the concept of it very much.  Daaveedee does a wonderful job bringing movies like this to the other side of the world for people like me to enjoy.  thanks, i would recommend this movie to others.
